OL,6,FThe court was told police believe
OL,7,Fthere is potential for more violence
OL,8,Fin the coming days with further anti-
OL,9,Fimmigration demonstrations planned.
OL,11,FA judge described scenes of disorder
OL,12,Fin the city at the weekend as
OL,13,F"absolutely disgraceful" as he refused
OL,14,Fbail to four men.
OL,16,FDeputy District Judge Liam McStay said
OL,17,Fthere were racist elements to the
OL,18,Fviolence and that the message had to
OL,19,Fbe sent that if "you allow yourself to
OL,20,Fbecome involved in this you will be
OL,21,Fremanded".
