OL,3,CFirst ministers unite to help build
OL,4,Cshared society after weekend riots
OL,6,FViolence flared after an an anti-
OL,7,Fimmigration demonstration left Belfast
OL,8,FCity Hall on Saturday.
OL,10,FThree police officers were injured in
OL,11,Fthe disturbances.
OL,13,FIn a joint statement, First Minister
OL,14,FMichelle O'Neill and deputy First
OL,15,FMinister Emma Little-Pengelly said:
OL,16,F"While people are entitled to take
OL,17,Fpart in peaceful protest there is no
OL,18,Fjustification for racism or for the
OL,19,Fviolence and intimidation that
OL,20,Foccurred on our streets on Saturday.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
