OL,6,F"Today we have spoken to the Chief
OL,7,FConstable and offered him our full
OL,8,Fsupport and we pledged to work to
OL,9,Fdeliver a shared, peaceful and
OL,10,Finclusive society.
OL,12,F"There must be a zero tolerance
OL,13,Fapproach to racism and wanton
OL,14,Fdestruction. Nobody should have to
OL,15,Flive in fear or threat of violence.
OL,17,F"Again, we would appeal to anyone with
